title: Oriental Art - India, Nepal and Tibet (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Pdf / 195 pages / English / 1970 Arco / 34.8 MB

Richly illustrated with photographs and line drawings this book is written in a clear and simple way which will enable the reader to invest wisely and obtain the greatest pleasure from collecting Oriental Art. The author, who has collected for many years, points out the pitfalls which may befall the amateur collector and gives useful tips in the recognition of forgeries
